<h3>End Game</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Death tokens
        <ul>
            <li>X = # of death tokens owned by player with the fewest</li>
            <li>all players discard X death tokens</li>
            <li>lose points based on table
                <div class="table table-40">
                    <div class="table-row">
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">1</div>
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">2</div>
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">3</div>
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">4</div>
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">5</div>
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">6</div>
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">7</div>
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">8</div>
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">9</div>
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">10</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="table-row">
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">1</div>
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">1</div>
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">2</div>
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">3</div>
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">5</div>
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">7</div>
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">9</div>
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">11</div>
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">13</div>
                        <div class="table-cell tc-1">15</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <br />
            </li>
            <li>-3 points per token in excess of 10</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li><img src="~/lib/Images/DinosaurWorld/icepack.png" class="icon" /> each ice age paddock can score 1 adjacency bonus <i>per mammal built</i></li>
    <li>$5 = 1 point</li>
</ul>

<h3>Reminders</h3>
<ul>
    <li><img src="~/lib/Images/DinosaurWorld/hybridpack.png" class="icon" /> hybrid dinos can count as either type for scoring objectives, even within the same paddock, but each dino still counts as 1 dino</li>
    <li><img src="~/lib/Images/DinosaurWorld/icepack.png" class="icon" /> ice age mammals count as 1 of the 3 dino types for purposes for game mechanics</li>
    <li>gain vp on some tiles immediately</li>
    <li>dino paddocks cannot be adjacent to dino paddocks (except Ice Age mammal paddocks)</li>
    <li>can never have duplicate tiles by name</li>
    <li>jeeple bonus is taken immediately, and again in income phase</li>
    <li>jeeple can not drive through a tile twice</li>
    <li>activating is optional but still costs movement</li>
    <li>dinos are required for activating a dino paddock</li>
    <li><img src="~/lib/Images/DinosaurWorld/waterpack.png" class="icon" /> add algae when placing tile (including setup draft) and adding dino; roll dice on Hire Worker phase</li>
</ul>

